{
  "stem": "5795.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And as we're going down the hill, he was telling us-- he went into-- what's the expression?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Into neutral, which is forbidden.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he told him it's forbidden.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He said, yes, sir, I know it's forbidden.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I'm ready to be put on a charge.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But why are you doing it?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I've got a brother in the merchant navy, and he's bringing over the oil and petrol, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he was thinking of him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the order, you know, that came through that the-- some of our-- our ships are being sunk.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So that was a moral lesson.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Right-- so what-- what happened?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Well, eventually we-- oh, then one or two of them were quite scholarly in Hebraic matters.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we had a little argument, a discussion, rather, on the grammatical point-- a grammatical point.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So I said let's-- let's solve it by going to Manchester.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It's only a 1/2 an hour's run or so.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I know Professor Manson of the Old Testament Department.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We arrived that Sunday afternoon, and he looked at us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He said, in the middle of a war, [LAUGHS] you guys are worried about a small grammatical point in the Hebrew language?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And he thought it was lovely.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then we all-- then we disappeared to our own particular units.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then I was sent to East Central District.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Dunstable.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Dunstable.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then there were three messes-- one for the general, and lieutenant colonels, and colonels, and one or two majors.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then the second was lieutenant colonels, and majors, and captains.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the third one was majors, captains, lieutenants, etc cetera.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was in the third mess.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But they said you got to find your own billet-- your own sleeping apartment.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I found a house not very, very far away, a home, of Mr.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
